import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Checkbox from './index'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"checkboxs"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#checkboxs"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Checkboxs`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Checkbox} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usages"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#basic-usages"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Basic usages`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Checkbox label="Aceitos os termos" fontSize="22px" />`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox 
    label="Aceitos os termos"
    fontSize="22px"
  />
</Playground></MDXTag>
